      <title>雪佛龙称以色列天然气业务过去曾遭受袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/chevron-says-israel-gas-operations-were-targeted-in-past-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司首席执行官迈克·沃思表示，在美国支持的停火计划上个月底生效之前，雪佛龙公司的以色列天然气业务就遭到了伊朗支持的真主党的攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/chevron-says-israel-gas-operations-were-targeted-in-past-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 20:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称其成功进行了一次太空发射，而该项目长期以来一直受到西方的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-06/urgent-iran-says-it-conducted-a-successful-space-launch-in-program-long-criticized-by-west</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴林麦纳麦（美联社）——国际原子能机构负责人周五警告说，伊朗已启动先进离心机的级联，准备“大幅”增加其近武器级铀库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-06/urgent-iran-says-it-conducted-a-successful-space-launch-in-program-long-criticized-by-west</guid>
